Die verschiedenen Erhebungsverfahren einschließlich der jeweiligen Stichprobengröße sind im Folgenden für alle beteiligten Länder aufgeführt:

Tschechische Republik: 1909, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview);
Dänemark: 1325, web based (self completion). Bei non-response: telephone interviews: CATI (Computer Assisted Telephone Interview) were used;
Estland: 1009, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview)/self-administered;
Finnland: 1243, postal (both directions), self-completion, paper and pencil or internet, web questionnaire;
Frankreich: 2017, self-completion, mail;
Großbritannien: 904, Das ISSP-Modul wird als self-completion questionnaire durchgeführt, vom Befragten nach dem face-to-face-Interview vervollständigt und vom Interviewer gesammelt  oder vom Befragten gesendet;
Kroatien: 1000, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview);
Ungarn: 1007, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview);
Irland: 1215, self-completed Postal Questionnaire with online option, Interactive self-administered questionnaire: CASI (Computer Assisted Self-Interview);
Israel: 1204, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview);
Island: 1082, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview) and Interactive self-administered questionnaire: CASI (Computer Assisted Self-Interview);
Japan: 1234, self-completion;
Litauen: 1194, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview);
Lettland: 1000, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview);
Norwegen: 1585, self-completion, web questionnaire;
Philippinen: 1200, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview);
Russland: 1516, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview);
Slowenien: 1010, CAPI (Computer Assisted Personal Interview);
Taiwan: 1952, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview) and CAPI (Computer Assisted Personal Interview);
Schweiz: 1237, CAPI (Computer Assisted Personal Interview);
Belgien: 2202, self-administered questionnaire: paper;
Deutschland: 1717, self-completion questionnaire (CASI), interviewer in attendance.
Background variables were asked face-to-face (CAPI).
Georgien: 1498, face-to-face interview; 
Indien: 1530, face-to-face interview; 
Korea (Süd): 1294, face-to-face interview; 
Mexiko: 1062, face-to-face interview; 
Portugal: 1001, face-to-face interviews (CAPI, with visuals);
Slovakei: 1156, pen and paper with visuals;
Süd Afrika: 2739, face-to-face interview;   
Spanien: 1225, face-to-face interview; 
Schweden: 1090, postal survey + lottery ticket;
Türkei: 1666, face-to-face interview; 
Vereinigte Staaten: 1274, face-to-face interview (CAPI), einige Fälle nachgefasst und am Telefon abgeschlossen

