Taiwan: 1952, face-to-face interview: PAPI (Paper and Pencil Interview) and CAPI (Computer Assisted Personal Interview); 
Switzerland: 1237, CAPI (Computer Assisted Personal Interview);
Belgium: 2202, self-administered questionnaire: paper;
Germany: 1717, self-completion questionnaire (CASI), interviewer in attendance.
Background variables were asked face-to-face (CAPI).
